X represents a radical derived from  EPSILON -caprolactone, of formula --(CH2)5 --C(O)--O--;


n, m and p represent, independently of each other, integers from 0 to 12, the sum of which is at least equal to 1 and does not exceed 12, and preferably is at least equal to 3 and does not exceed 10;


